OL,3,CMan tried to kill special constable in
OL,4,C'calculated attack' at railway station
OL,6,FA man who stabbed a special constable
OL,7,Fin the neck in a "calculated attack"
OL,8,Fat a busy railway station has been
OL,9,Ffound guilty of attempted murder.
OL,11,FBritish Transport Police (BTP) said
OL,12,FRussell Smith, 54, was stopped after a
OL,13,Fcolleague alerted by the officer's
OL,14,Fscreams used his captor spray to
OL,15,Frestrain him.
OL,17,FThe "exceptionally violent" attack
OL,18,Fhappened at Preston Railway Station
OL,19,Fduring the Radio 2 in the Park weekend
OL,20,Fon 7 September 2024.
