OL,3,CMan tried to kill special constable in
OL,4,C'calculated attack' at railway station
OL,6,FAccording to BTP, Smith first
OL,7,Fapproached the officer while he was
OL,8,Fadvising members of the public on
OL,9,Ftheir travel plans.
OL,11,FHe followed him out of the station
OL,12,Fthen, as the officer returned, Smith
OL,13,Fpulled a kitchen knife from his
OL,14,Fpocket, raised it above his head and
OL,15,Fran towards him.
