OL,3,CMan tried to kill special constable in
OL,4,C'calculated attack' at railway station
OL,6,FBritish Transport Police say the
OL,7,Fofficer sustained a puncture wound to
OL,8,Ftheir spine and that "it is only by
OL,9,Fsheer luck" that this injury did not
OL,10,Fcause life-threatening or life-
OL,11,Fchanging injuries.
OL,13,FSmith, 54, of Shakespeare Road,
OL,14,FPreston, who denied all charges in
OL,15,Fcourt, was found guilty of attempted
OL,16,Fmurder and possession of a bladed
OL,17,Farticle and will be sentenced on
OL,18,FMonday, 14 April.
