OL,3,CMan tried to kill special constable in
OL,4,C'calculated attack' at railway station
OL,6,FAssistant Chief Constable Charlie
OL,7,FDoyle said: "This was an exceptionally
OL,8,Fviolent, shocking and calculated
OL,9,Fattack on a uniformed police officer
OL,10,Fas they were simply doing their job.
OL,12,F"It is a testament to the character of
OL,13,Fthe officer involved that he has now
OL,14,Freturned to duty and remains
OL,15,Fdetermined to fulfil his role as a
OL,16,Fspecial constable, protecting the
OL,17,Fpublic and keeping the railway safe."
